@59   = ~Elminster the Bird~
@60   = ~Elminster is Geraldo's tame bird, although even he does not know the exact species. The bird has a wise look and an exceptional aversion to gibberlings. As soon as he senses one he will call a loud 'Kiwitt'.

Without the bird, it would be impossible to track down the gibberlings in the cellars and sewers, so take good care of him.~
